                    <p class="utterance">... furthermore, I was [working] in an industry, in the paper branch &#226; in the paper industry.</p>
                                                                                                <b>David Boder</b>
                    <p class="utterance">Why did you, ah, relocate to France?</p>
                                                                                                <b>Karl Josephy</b>
                    <p class="utterance">I relocated to France because through the revolution, the Nazi revolution in Austria, I was threatened in my profession, in my further intellectual progress as well as politically.</p>
                                                                                                <b>David Boder</b>
