                    <p class="utterance">Yes. [tape break]</p>
                                                                                                <b>David Boder</b>
                    <p class="utterance">Now, Mr. Josephy, if someone asked you, or if you would write a book, what would you want to tell us as the main points of your experiences, from (19)38 until the liberation?</p>
                                                                                                <b>Karl Josephy</b>
                    <p class="utterance">As main points, I would without doubt tell you of my dangers and my suffering that I endured .from the moment of my arrest ...</p>
                                                                                                <b>David Boder</b>
                    <p class="utterance">Yes ...</p>
