                    <p class="utterance">... which at the same time affected my wife.</p>
                                                                                                <b>David Boder</b>
                    <p class="utterance">So do you want to begin then? Do you want to begin how things were in Paris, and how the whole misfortune, ah --- how you were, ah, gradually pulled out of your quiet life?</p>
